  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fruits and Shade for Schools (FSS) Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Future Connect Ghana will create 20 orchards with 10 varieties of fruit and shade trees in 20 schools, 5 public playgrounds, and farmlands. This project will plant 10,000 fruit and shade trees to provide over 20,000 children with nutritious fruits to eat and play in a safe environment whilst away from their parents. The project will also benefit 1000+ farmers by planting trees on farmlands to provide resiliency to climate change and alternative livelihood to the underserved farming communities.</narrative>
  </description>
